description: Describes the termination policies supported by Amazon EC2 Auto Scaling. For more information, see Configure termination policies for Amazon EC2 Auto Scaling in the Amazon EC2 Auto Scaling User Guide.

nested_items.name: TerminationPolicyTypes
nested_items.description: The termination policies supported by Amazon EC2 Auto Scaling: OldestInstance, OldestLaunchConfiguration, NewestInstance, ClosestToNextInstanceHour, Default, OldestLaunchTemplate, and AllocationStrategy.
